ANGELA BASSET Onscreen, whether in ``Malcolm X,'' or ``Boyz 'N the
Hood,'' actress Angela Bassett is always larger than life. In ``How
Stella Got Her Groove Back,'' she finds a softer edge. Based on
Terry McMillan's sexy bestseller, the film is about a successful
woman's Jamaica vacation romp with a younger man. Interview by
Louise Farr. From W magazine. 1,500 words + photos.
