closings of several streets in the heart of Times Square, and who
may ultimately pay. By Leslie Eaton.
</P>
<P>
   NY-SCAFFOLD-DISMANTLE (New York) _ How they're taking down the
scaffolding and tower. By David W. Dunlap.
