   NYHAN-COLUMN (Undated) -- John Knox's heirs sow hatred in
Northern Ireland. By David Nyhan.
</P>
<P>
   MCNAMARA-COLUMN (Undated) -- It is an election year and health
care reform is back with a vengeance on the public agenda. By
Eileen McNamara.
</P>
