past two decades creating animation for MTV, Hanna-Barbera Studios
and Nickelodeon, Fred Seibert thinks he knows. And over the next
few months, he'll try to prove it, with a new series of one-off
animated shorts he commissioned from a group of writer-directors
whose work he admires. By David Bloom. 
. 

