<P>
   SOCAL-BIG-BOSSES (Los Angeles) _ The largest employers in
Southern California are a mix of public and private entities, with
the companies coming from diverse industries, according to a report
released by the Los Angeles Economic Development Corp. By Enrique
Rivero.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-07-22-98 1752EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
