theater piece performed by the Philip Glass Ensemble.
</P>
<P>
   Tuesday, April 13 &AMP; Wednesday, April 14: St. Petersburg State
Ice Ballet presents ``Romeo and Juliet on Ice.''
</P>
<P>
   Wednesday, April 21: The Acting Company presents Shakespeare's
``Twelfth Night.''
