<P>
   MICROSOFT-GLASER (Undated) Former Microsoft executive and
RealNetworks founder Rob Glaser is among the witnesses who will
testify about Microsoft today to the Senate Judiciary Committee.
Analysts say he might talk about Microsoft's attempts to steal
customers by offering sweet deals on other products _ a tactic
similar to those at the heart of the antitrust complaints against
the company. RealNetworks say Glaser's testimony will be very
specific, but give no clues other than that. Microsoft has decided
not to participate.
