after the committee declined Wednesday to send Daryl Jones's
nomination for Secretary of the Air Force to the floor without a
recommendation. Others, from left, are Sens. Robert Smith, John
McCain, John Warner and Carl Levin. (Paul Hosefros/New York Times
Photo)
