<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-SCI-CLONED-MICE-NYT, which moved
in ``a'' news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``If we follow scientific protocol it could take five to 10
years before in vitro fertilization clinics add human cloning to
their repertoires.
</P>
<P>
   _DR. LEE SILVER, a geneticist at Princeton University.
</P>
